mily of spherically symmetric equilibria\ncaptures all spherically symmetric equilibria of the approximate system.\nHowever within the full model, this family is embedded in a larger family of\nspherically symmetric solutions. For the approximate system, we prove that all\nequilibrium bubbles are spherically symmetric, by an application of\nAlexandrov's theorem on closed surfaces of constant mean curvature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jul 2022 18:11:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Jul 2022 16:55:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 19:51:14 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 2 Jan 2023 06:18:46 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2023 15:47:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-07"}
