d scalability. We checked its reliability\nagainst a 2D analogue of sod shock tube test and tests specific to PPDs that\nincludes Rossby wave instability (RWI), streaming instability (SI), dust\ncapture by a vortex and dust settling. We release this code under the terms of\nthe CeCILL2 Licence and make it publicly available.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 Jul 2022 11:33:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2023 06:38:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-30"}
